        <updateDate>2007-04-07T14:58:44Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Family Friendly Employers Act of 2007 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to expand the tax exclusion for employer-provided educational assistance to include assistance provided to dependents of an employee. Limits the annual amount of the exclusion for such dependents to $2,500.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
